**[scene tag — Deciding to Explore the Air Temple]**
- The party debates whether to descend or explore the Air Temple's passages while Calmer is absent, deeply injured and taken upstairs by Dren Halveth.
- One of Dren's mercenaries is sent up as backup, left behind to guard the doorway since they are "anything but stealthy."
- Zephyr leads ahead; Sequoia and Zinnia follow toward a southwest passageway.

**[GM]** — explaining the strategic situation
> "they're very determined for this fight to end, and given that your objective is fundamentally to kill… to destroy the temple, having them slaughter each other is not a bad outcome. Does that make sense?"

**[Zephyr]**
> "So how do we keep those tight [inaudible — probable "corners"]?"

**[GM]**
> "these are all chaotic evil… chaotic evil, individuals, right? Those chaotic evil individuals, their main motivation is power, so pretty much all you have to do is let them keep fighting and periodically stab one in the back, and the battle… the battle ends. Does that make sense?"

